rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0001
rows.name:
There's a feeling of unease that's
been spreading through Gula- in
the White Chair, especially.

rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0002
rows.name:
We'll soon get orders from
the chief to return home.

rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0003
rows.name:
In such turbulent times, we
must endeavor to maintain
friendly relations with Superbia.

rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0004
rows.name:
We plan to continue aligning with
Superbia as far as is possible.

rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0005
rows.name:
We Gulan plan to throw everything
we have at supporting the Iirans.

rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0006
rows.name:
There's an element of self-interest to
this, of course, but they're people, so
we must offer them our assistance.

rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0007
rows.name:
There's value in helping those
in trouble, no matter their
social status or background...

rows.label: tlk70000089_03_msg0008
rows.name:
That's a lesson I have learned
directly from your example.
